<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Future Simple</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/learn-grammar/future-simple.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,300..800;1,300..800&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900&family=Sour+Gummy:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Tinos:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        .modal {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            z-index: 1;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .modal-content {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 500px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .close-btn {
            float: right;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>There is - There are</h1>
        <table>
            <tr class="row1">
                <td class="first-column">Positive</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal1')">There <span>is</span></td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal2')">There <span>are</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="row2">
                <td class="first-column">Negative</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal3')">There <span>is not</span> <br>There <span>isn't</span></td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal4')">There <span>are not</span> <br>There <span>aren't</span></td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="row3">
                <td class="first-column">Questions</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal5')"><span>Is</span> there...?</td>
                <td class="button-box" onclick="showExamples('modal6')"><span>Are</span> there...?</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="@Url.Action("TestDetails", "LearnGrammar", new { id = Model.TopicID })" class="btn btn-primary">Start Test</a>
        </div>

        <div id="modal1" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal1')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (There is - Affirmative)</h2>
                <p>- There is a book on the table.</p>
                <p>- There is a cat under the bed.</p>
                <p>- There is a message for you.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal2" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal2')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (There are - Affirmative)</h2>
                <p>- There are books on the shelf.</p>
                <p>- There are two chairs in the room.</p>
                <p>- There are many stars in the sky.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal3" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal3')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (There is not - Negative)</h2>
                <p>- There isn't a pen on the desk.</p>
                <p>- There isn't a car in the garage.</p>
                <p>- There isn't any milk in the fridge.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal4" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal4')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (There are not - Negative)</h2>
                <p>- There aren't any apples in the basket.</p>
                <p>- There aren't enough chairs for everyone.</p>
                <p>- There aren't any students in the classroom.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal5" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal5')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (Is there...? - Questions)</h2>
                <p>- Is there a problem?</p>
                <p>- Is there a restaurant nearby?</p>
                <p>- Is there a phone in the room?</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="modal6" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-btn" onclick="closeModal('modal6')">&times;</span>
                <h2>Examples (Are there...? - Questions)</h2>
                <p>- Are there any questions?</p>
                <p>- Are there any books in the bag?</p>
                <p>- Are there enough plates for everyone?</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

        <script>
            function showExamples(modalId) {
                document.getElementById(modalId).style.display = "flex";
            }
            function closeModal(modalId) {
                document.getElementById(modalId).style.display = "none";
            }
        </script>
</body>
</html>
